					<![CDATA[
						 <p>This is a great example of a scip being humorous without crossing the line into -J territory. The line I found funniest is also the most deadpan:</p> <blockquote> <p>Note that this phenomenon is purely visual in nature, and <strong>no actual alteration of the stars is taking place.</strong></p> </blockquote> <p>I would hope not!</p> 
