					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-5494639#post-3740316</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-5494639/scp-3186#post-3740316</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Fri, 16 Mar 2018 10:07:33 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Znyra</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>3775625</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I absolutely adore this.</p> <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">Spoilers?&nbsp;idk&nbsp;it's&nbsp;my&nbsp;headcanon&nbsp;now</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">–&nbsp;hide&nbsp;block</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <p>It just shows the story of a teenager trying to use occult magic to ask a girl he likes to attend prom with him. Of course, he skims it and doesn't know how to cancel the ritual once he is done, so he continues to say things which he thinks would end the message, but they're only translated into the message as parts of it.</p> </div> </div> </div> <p>You have easily earned my upvote.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
					<item>
